acceptance_criteria: "--updated-after/--updated-before and --created-after/--created-before accept ISO+relative; appear in filters block; wired into update-many, pm context, and MCP contracts."
value: pm list has only --deadline-before/after; agents doing incremental 'what changed since' sync must fetch all 900+ items and filter client-side. Add updated/created date-window filters (reuse resolveIsoOrRelative).
parent: pm-mpbb
resolution: "Added --updated-after/-before/--created-after/-before to runList, list* commands, update-many/close-many --filter-* family, and MCP pm_list contracts; signed-relative + ISO; 100%-tested"
