comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-04T16:17:23.367Z",maintainer-agent,"Shipped on branch cli-incremental-context-and-bulk-ops-20260604. Added --updated-after/--updated-before/--created-after/--created-before to runList + all list* commands + MCP pm_list contracts. Reuses the shared signed-relative resolver (resolveIsoOrRelative): ISO timestamps (primary 'changed since last window' case) or signed offsets (-2h/-7d past, +1d future; units h/d/w/m, m=months, no minutes unit). Raw inputs echoed in filters block. Also wired into update-many/close-many --filter-updated-*/--filter-created-* family."
close_reason: Delivered incremental updated/created date-window filters on list + bulk-ops + MCP
